      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced onion</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> </strong>and<strong> half </strong>the<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
