    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim the ends from your <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then finely slice</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong> and a splash of <strong>water </strong>and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced Brussels sprouts</strong> to the pan with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 7-8 min further or until softened</p>",
