    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut into 1 square per person</p><p>Transfer the <strong>pastry</strong> <strong>square[s]</strong> to a baking tray lined with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong> and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Top the centre of <strong>pastry square[s] </strong>with the <strong>Brussels sprout &</strong> <strong>garam</strong> <strong>masala</strong> <strong>tart filling</strong></p>",
